                      Schedule Details
                      </h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="panel-body tab-content" style="background: white !important;">
                    
                      <br /><span style="font-size: 18px !important;">
                        <strong>Day:</strong>
                        <%= @schedule.day.strftime("%A") %>
                      </span><br /><br />
